# Input

```html
<div
  test="content must break if attributes break"
  explanation="This group of attributes should break and become multiline."
  details="The content must do the same, despite it being short."
>short content</div>

```


# Formatted

```html
<div
	test="content must break if attributes break"
	explanation="This group of attributes should break and become multiline."
	details="The content must do the same, despite it being short."
>
	short content
</div>

```
